==========
Secure EC2
==========


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/secure_ec2.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/secure_ec2

.. image:: https://github.com/avishayil/secure_ec2/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg
